                              Featured Programs

   Vietnam Veterans Memorial

   Welcome Veterans!
   An overview of our programs: Learn about the California Veterans
   Memorial, Cal-Vet Home Loan, Women Veterans and other benefits and
   programs from CDVA.

   Cal-Vet Homebuyers

   Cal-Vet Home Loans
   For over 75 years Cal-Vet has been offering veterans the best home loan
   value in California. Current Cal-Vet interest rates

   Properties for Sale
   Purchase a home from Cal-Vet - a good deal for you and California's
   Veterans.

   Veterans License Plate

   Veterans Licence Plates
   Proudly display special veterans license plates on all your family
   vehicles.

   Homeless Veteran

   Homeless Veterans Resources
   A Hand Up, Not a Hand Out: Check out this new section in CDVA's web
   site for the latest news on homelessness, current information on Stand
   Downs, an update on state and federal legislation, plus links to more
   than three dozen service providers in California.




